{
  "id": "59dd8b0a87257c001201f319",
  "title": "天は人の上に人を造らず人の下に人を造らず",
  "created": 1507691277,
  "updated": 1608524740,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "59dd8b0a87257c001201f319",
      "text": "天は人の上に人を造らず人の下に人を造らず",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507691277,
      "updated": 1507691299
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8b0eaff09e0000e3c7ac",
      "text": "[福沢諭吉]の[学問のすすめ http://www.aozora.gr.jp/cards/000296/files/47061_29420.html]のつかみの一言。ここだけ切り出して「人は[平等]」という主張に使われることがあるが福沢諭吉の意図はそこではない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507691278,
      "updated": 1608524708
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8e86aff09e0000e3c7ba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507692166,
      "updated": 1507692166
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8e23aff09e0000e3c7b8",
      "text": "学問のすすめ冒頭2段落の要約",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507692067,
      "updated": 1507692252
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8cabaff09e0000e3c7b2",
      "text": " 天は人の上に人を造らず人の下に人を造らず",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507691692,
      "updated": 1507697030
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8cdcaff09e0000e3c7b3",
      "text": " だけど広くこの人間世界を見渡すと、雲と泥くらい格差がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507691740,
      "updated": 1507697030
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8cfcaff09e0000e3c7b4",
      "text": " 賢人と愚人の差は学ぶか学ばないかによって生じる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507691772,
      "updated": 1507697030
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8d2baff09e0000e3c7b5",
      "text": " 難しい仕事をする人が身分の重い人。易しい仕事をする人が身分の軽い人。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507691820,
      "updated": 1507697030
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8d55aff09e0000e3c7b6",
      "text": " 身分が重ければ、家が富む。下々の人からは手が届かないように見えるかもしれないが、元々は学ぶ力があるかどうかによってできた差である。天が定めたわけではない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507691861,
      "updated": 1507697030
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8dd1aff09e0000e3c7b7",
      "text": " 人は生まれながらに貴賤・貧富があるのではない。学んで物事をよく知る者は貴人となり富人となり、無学なる者は貧人となり下人となる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507691985,
      "updated": 1507697030
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8e35aff09e0000e3c7b9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507692085,
      "updated": 1507692085
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8b5aaff09e0000e3c7af",
      "text": "つまり「今の世界が平等である」とも「平等であるべき」とも言っていない。「今の世界は不平等だが、それは学ぶ力によってできた差である」と言っている。タイトルの通り「学問のすすめ」なのだ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507691355,
      "updated": 1507692195
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8f1daff09e0000e3c7be",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507692318,
      "updated": 1507692318
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8f1daff09e0000e3c7bd",
      "text": "青空文庫で読める: http://www.aozora.gr.jp/cards/000296/files/47061_29420.html",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507692318,
      "updated": 1507692325
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8f56aff09e0000e3c7c0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507692374,
      "updated": 1507692374
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8f55aff09e0000e3c7bf",
      "text": "要約の続き",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507692374,
      "updated": 1507692378
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8f59aff09e0000e3c7c1",
      "text": "\t学問とは難しい文字を知っているとか、詩を作るとかの、実用的でない文学のことを言っているのではない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507692378,
      "updated": 1507692440
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8facaff09e0000e3c7c3",
      "text": " そういう実のない学問は次にして、まずは[実学]を学ぶべき。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507692460,
      "updated": 1608524740
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd92d3aff09e0000e3c7c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693267,
      "updated": 1507693267
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd8f68aff09e0000e3c7c2",
      "text": "\t2 人は同等",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507692393,
      "updated": 1507693275
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd92dbaff09e0000e3c7c5",
      "text": " 3",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693275,
      "updated": 1507693285
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd92e4aff09e0000e3c7c6",
      "text": " \t国は同等",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693285,
      "updated": 1507693287
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd92e7aff09e0000e3c7c7",
      "text": "  一身独立して一国独立する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693287,
      "updated": 1507693301
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd92f5aff09e0000e3c7c8",
      "text": " 4 学者の職分",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693302,
      "updated": 1507693333
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd9315aff09e0000e3c7c9",
      "text": " 5,6 知識人向けの話",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693333,
      "updated": 1507693355
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd932aaff09e0000e3c7ca",
      "text": " 7 国民の職分",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693355,
      "updated": 1507693402
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd9358aff09e0000e3c7cb",
      "text": " 8 儒教的な上下関係の否定",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693402,
      "updated": 1507693432
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd9377aff09e0000e3c7cc",
      "text": " 9 学問の二種類の目的",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693432,
      "updated": 1507693455
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd938eaff09e0000e3c7cd",
      "text": " 10 9の続き",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693455,
      "updated": 1507693477
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd93a4aff09e0000e3c7ce",
      "text": " 11 8の続き",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693477,
      "updated": 1507693490
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd93b1aff09e0000e3c7cf",
      "text": " 12",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693490,
      "updated": 1507693527
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd93d7aff09e0000e3c7d0",
      "text": "  演説をすすめる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693528,
      "updated": 1507693534
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd93deaff09e0000e3c7d2",
      "text": "  向上心",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693534,
      "updated": 1507693546
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd93e9aff09e0000e3c7d3",
      "text": " 13",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693546,
      "updated": 1507693547
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd93ebaff09e0000e3c7d4",
      "text": "  怨望はよくない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693547,
      "updated": 1507693565
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd93fdaff09e0000e3c7d5",
      "text": "  言論の自由が大事",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693565,
      "updated": 1507693582
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd940daff09e0000e3c7d6",
      "text": " 14",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693582,
      "updated": 1507693583
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd9410aff09e0000e3c7d7",
      "text": "  長期的な計画と棚卸",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693584,
      "updated": 1507693605
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd9425aff09e0000e3c7d8",
      "text": "  監督と保護は両輪",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693605,
      "updated": 1507693622
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd9436aff09e0000e3c7d9",
      "text": " 15",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693622,
      "updated": 1507693624
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd9437aff09e0000e3c7da",
      "text": "  懐疑主義",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693624,
      "updated": 1507693636
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd9443aff09e0000e3c7db",
      "text": " 16",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693636,
      "updated": 1507693638
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd9445aff09e0000e3c7dc",
      "text": "  独立を守ること",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693638,
      "updated": 1507693666
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd9461aff09e0000e3c7dd",
      "text": "  [自己評価と実力の一致]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693666,
      "updated": 1608472549
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd9471aff09e0000e3c7de",
      "text": " 17",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693681,
      "updated": 1507693683
    },
    {
      "id": "59dd9472aff09e0000e3c7df",
      "text": "  他人からの評価を得る方法",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1507693683,
      "updated": 1507693710
    },
    {
      "id": "5fdf57deaff09e00004d0303",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1608472543,
      "updated": 1608472543
    },
